com.morpheus.sdk.monitoring

Class CheckType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheus.sdk.monitoring.CheckType

  • public class CheckType
extends java.lang.Object
    A Model representation of a Morpheus Check Type It is used by GSON Decoder to convert JSON of the following structure into a java based Object. 
    
   "checkType": {
    "class": "com.morpheus.monitoring.MonitorCheckType",
    "code": "webGetCheck",
    "createIncident": true,
    "defaultInterval": 60000,
    "execMethod": null,
    "execService": null,
    "iconPath": null,
    "iconType": "upload",
    "id": 1,
    "inUptime": true,
    "inputTemplate": "/monitorTemplates/input/webCheck",
    "metricName": "response",
    "name": "Web Check",
    "pushOnly": false,
    "queueName": "morpheusWebGetCheck",
    "script": null,
    "statusTemplate": "/monitorTemplates/status/webCheck",
    "tunnelSupported": true,
    "viewTemplate": "/monitorTemplates/view/webCheck"
  }
